item.title: Spawn
item.description: Welcome to spawn, everyone who joins the server will see this when they join. The Tower The bones of this building was my first project in the server after clearing an Area around spawn, to the top of the old build limit this has many floors for people to claim and put what they want. Pride Robot A Nice rainbow Robot, first community project! Aquarium The Aquarium (Closed For Maintenance) - Community Member Built

item.title: Alexandria
item.description: The maze Just outside of Alexandria is the Maze and the Sheep The Pyramid A Small Pyramid and its Cat friend The Lighthouse of Alexandria

item.title: Library Of Alexandria
item.description: A Wonderful Mega-build of a library / museum Many hours and Many people went into this build. The entrance with the lighthouse in the background Grand Staircase A Staircase hidden away among the bookshelves The Chandelier Art The Kitten Guards of the Library A History of Armour and Fauna The Vault a Near impenetrable vault to store the special books The Books The Docks For those whom wish to arrive by boat

item.title: New Zone 2024
item.description: We started a new survival play through in 2024, here is some of the stuff Fishes House JJs House My House Auto Farms This has Cane, Bamboo, Kelp and a very awful smelter New Theme Park Name TBD, Think something that makes Machland look tiny With a treehouse Mega Farm 60k~ capacity Over 300k Blocks moved All in survival Video coming soon â„¢

item.description: Not much to say here, the new build height tower was built in survival though… Apart from the super vault

item.title: Mach Land
item.description: Mach Land is rollercoaster park and entertainment zone.. Various community and group builds here. Entrance and kids coaster Machyear blimp, fireworks & Space Mountain Collapsed Coaster A Failed baritone build, but it looks cool Ride Entrances Mach Land Zoo A Short Rail (under construction) ride away from Machland is the Machland zoo, housed in a mega pyramid.

item.title: Others
item.description: This is for impressive stand alone builds, where its 1/2 buildings not with an area around it of other things.. Zoo 1 The first zoo built in the server Dutch Government Building A Wonderful Build by Gorby Dry dock TrapHouse A building worthy of its own page, but yet to be challenged so all you get it the outside

item.title: JJs Towns
item.description: JJ Has many towns around and many one off mega builds, here are some of them that aren’t part of another area (or are there own distinct area) Town 1 JJ’s 2/3 project, the first two have mainly been dismantled or rebuilt over time.

item.title: Trex Land
item.description: An Area a few blocks from spawn, containing mostly Trex’s /Related creations. Rawr means i love you in dinosaur Dino art with the hotel in the background. Trex’s House The Hotel A nice multi bedroom hotel at the top of a hill with a wonderful view and nearby rail connections Mini Farm Just outside of trex land is a micro farm made by me, nothing special but quite pretty
